{"url": "https://ew.com/movies/2017/08/23/beauty-and-the-beast-emma-watson-netflix/", "text": "The tale as old as time is coming to Netflix.\n\nThe live-action adaptation of the Walt Disney Pictures animated classic Beauty and the Beast arrives at the streaming service on Sept. 19. The movie, which stars Emma Watson and Dan Stevens in the titular roles, was released in theaters in March and grossed over $1.2 billion worldwide, thereby becoming the highest-grossing live-action musical movie in history as well as the highest grossing film of 2017.\n\nOn Wednesday, Netflix announced all the titles coming to and leaving the online distributor in September with plenty of \u201990s nostalgia including Dead Poets Society and Pulp Fiction as well as an assortment of Disney flicks such as Mulan and Hercules and a slew of Netflix originals. See the full list here.", "images": ["https://ewedit.files.wordpress.com/2019/06/little-women.jpg", "https://ewedit.files.wordpress.com/2019/07/point-blank-1-2000.jpg?crop=0px%2C0px%2C2000px%2C1050px&resize=1200%2C630", "https://ewedit.files.wordpress.com/2019/06/hulu.jpg", "https://ewedit.files.wordpress.com/2019/07/secret-obsession.jpg?crop=0px%2C0px%2C3200px%2C1680px&resize=1200%2C630", "https://ewedit.files.wordpress.com/2017/09/lennykravitz.jpg?w=768", "https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/c94654c862ed2e07d803b3fe49b1e82a?s=300&d=blank&r=g", "https://ewedit.files.wordpress.com/2019/06/viola-davis-chadwick-boseman.jpg", "https://ewedit.files.wordpress.com/2019/06/janet-mock.jpg?crop=0px%2C34px%2C2700px%2C1419px&resize=1200%2C630", "https://ew.com/img/icons/generic-image.svg", "https://ewedit.files.wordpress.com/2019/01/thelionking5c2f98925cc7b.jpg", "https://ewedit.files.wordpress.com/2019/07/gettyimages-1154698428.jpg", "https://ewedit.files.wordpress.com/2018/10/celebrity-binge.jpg?w=768", "https://ewedit.files.wordpress.com/2017/11/rolestout.jpg?w=768", "https://ewedit.files.wordpress.com/2019/06/leaving-netflix.jpg", "https://ewedit.